title: Big Brother USA 9 Live Feeds - 03-18-08
description:
Big Brother USA Live Feeds - 03/18/08 - xx2000xx

For youtube vids + exclusive content go to -  <a href="
http://bbcouchpotatoes.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://bbcouchpotatoes.blogspot.com/</a>

I promise I&#039;ll get all my usenet posts up tomorrow.

Tons of last minute campaigning and Josh building up some steam because he&#039;s going to go ballistic on Shelia tomorrow. It should be a great HOH and drama after. If he does go off on Sheila and her side doesn&#039;t win HOH I could see her asking for her DOR for sure.

Part 1 - 22 min
Josh talks about the vote and how the operation is going, then James calls Sheila out - Sheila/Nat/Chelsia talk. Chelia does her plan of thinking she will vote out Ryan and they are falling for it.

Part 2 - 18 min
It&#039;s the Adam show. Adam talks about the game + other stuff? Don&#039;t remember it that well.

Part 3 - 24 min
Here we go. Josh is steaming and ready to go off on sheila - Sheila talks about Josh and how if he goes off her 3 brothers will kick his ass - Josh fuming some more.

Part 4 - 26 min
Non-stop drama of Josh. We needed some good drama as the feeds have been slow the past few days.

Part 5 - 20 min
More action from all the drama.

Part 6 - 15 min
Josh goes on a Sheila rant + Nat prays to God for HOH.

Part 7 - 19 min
Sheila/Adam talk. Some funny stuff here.

Part 8 - 28 min
Chelsia sneaks up to the HOH to talk about the operation and how things have gone the past day - Matt does his last stand and begs for his safety.
